<subSubSection pageId="27" pageNumber="28" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,153,1223]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,1125,1151]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Etymology:</emphasis>
From the Latin words “fere” (nearly) and “nudum” (bare) in allusion to the species’ metasoma that is very sparsely hairy.
</paragraph>
